### Hadith 1:821

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

Once Allah's Apostle delayed the 'Isha' prayer till 'Umar informed him
that the women and children had slept. Then Allah's Apostle came out and
said: "None from amongst the dwellers of earth have prayed this prayer
except you." In those days none but the people of Medina prayed.

